Iyada oo daraasadda ee Venus oo dhan qorraxda ee 1761 yimid cilmiga Ruush Mikhail Lomonosov soo gabagabeeyey in meeraha ku lahaa jawi in uu ahaa ugu yaraan sida ballaaran , sida dhulku . [ 12 ] Dhawr tobanaan sano kadib , Johann Hieronymus Schröter helitaanka marqaatiyo more of its jawi

